# Example shellcheck config for the checkup `shellcheck` check.
#
# Copy to your project root as `.shellcheckrc`.
# One disabled rule per line — keep a reason next to each so the suppression
# stays honest.

# SC1091: shellcheck can't follow `source` targets resolved at runtime
# (dynamic paths, vendored files). Disable only if that noise is unavoidable.
disable=SC1091
